    Classes provide implementations of commands commonly used by plug-ins.

    Essential classes that interfaces directly with Spigot.
    com.karusmc.xmc.util
    Collection of utility classes for use in commands.
    com.karusmc.xmc.xml
    Classes used to parse XML Documents.
    com.karusmc.xmc.xml.nodes
